The service at this Subway is simply amazing. I realized I had forgotten my wallet when I went to pay for my sandwich and asked them to hold it for me while I ran home to grab it. I left and returned as quickly as I could, at which point they asked me if I’d like them to make me a new one. I thought that was kind, but unnecessary. I then sat down to eat, and they then offered me a drink free of charge since I might be hot from running to grab my wallet. To to try and repay the gesture a little, I decided to buy a couple of cookies, and they then gave me an extra one for free. I’ll definitely return here, even if just for the amazingly friendly service.
